TITLE: Enabling RFC6587 Auto-Detection in syslog-ng Source
DESCRIPTION: This configuration snippet demonstrates how to enable automatic detection of RFC6587 octet-count based framing for a `syslog()` source in `syslog-ng`. Using `transport(auto)` within the source definition allows the server to adapt to senders using octet-counting, potentially resolving protocol mismatches.
SOURCE: https://github.com/syslog-ng/syslog-ng/blob/develop/news/feature-5322.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: plaintext
CODE:
```
transport(auto)
```

