TITLE: Adding Unit Test for Transport Mapper (CMake)
DESCRIPTION: This CMake snippet registers a unit test target named 'test-transport-mapper', sets its dependency on the 'afsocket' component, and includes the required source files 'test-transport-mapper.c' and 'transport-mapper-lib.c'. Requires the Criterion testing framework and that afsocket is available as a dependency in the build. This configuration enables automated execution of transport mapper tests through the CMake testing infrastructure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/syslog-ng/syslog-ng/blob/develop/modules/afsocket/tests/CMakeLists.txt#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: CMake
CODE:
```
add_unit_test(CRITERION
  TARGET test-transport-mapper
  DEPENDS afsocket
  SOURCES test-transport-mapper.c transport-mapper-lib.c)
```

