TITLE: Setting Compile Flags for PatternDB Target in CMake
DESCRIPTION: Sets compile flags for the `patterndb` target. It adds `-fPIC` for position-independent code, suitable for shared libraries, and `-Wno-pointer-sign` to suppress specific compiler warnings related to pointer sign mismatches, particularly noted in the radix tree implementation.
